2}, {\"ngram\": \"this romance\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisians whom The Straits Times spoke to have expressed mixed feelings about the July 26 to Aug 11 Games.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Straits Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"mixed feelings\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"the July\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug 11 Games\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some welcome the branding, tourism dollars and eyeballs that come with hosting the Olympics, while others point to the downsides of having a mega event in the heart of the city.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the branding, tourism dollars\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"eyeballs\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"the downsides\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"a mega event\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photographer Johanna Liscio noted that it is the perfect opportunity to showcase her home, though it has impacted her business.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anjouan\", \"score\": 0.9998162543073644, \"rank\": 0.00018377942341728264, \"text\": \"Johanna\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anjouan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anjouan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the perfect opportunity\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"her home\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"her business\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old, who specialises in vacation, proposal and engagement photography under the Instagram handle@paris.spirit,typically gets about 10 bookings weekly, but business has dipped by about 60 per cent during this period, with iconic landmarks such as the Eiffel Tower cordoned off.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"vacation\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"proposal\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"engagement\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"photography\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"the Instagram handle@paris.spirit\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"about 60 per cent\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"this period\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"iconic landmarks\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The majority of her clients are tourists from Asia, Europe and North America.\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The majority\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"her clients\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"Asia\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"North America\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"Paris is one of the most visited cities in the world and it's great for us, for the economy, for tourism to host the Games.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most visited cities\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"the economy\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1487}, {\"ngram\": \"tourism\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For my job, I am not as happy as I thought I'd be - it's a bit stressful that I have to adapt to the situation every day, it's a bit more complicated than expected.\\\"\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my job\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the lead-up to the Olympics, some Parisians have voiced their unhappiness over having to endure months of disruption as the cityprepared for the quadrennial event.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"some Parisians\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"their unhappiness\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"disruption\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"the cityprepared\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"the quadrennial event\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Road closures and construction have inconvenienced locals, increasing travelling time within the city significantly.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Road closures\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"travelling time\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another concern is rising prices during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another concern\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"prices\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, the price of a single metro ticket has increased from \\u20ac2.15 (S$3) to \\u20ac4 from July 20 to Sept 8.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"a single metro ticket\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u20ac2.15 (S$3\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"Sept\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Businesses in Olympic security zoneshave also struggled, with some restaurant owners experiencing 80 per cent fewer customers owing to stricter security measures.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Businesses\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic security zoneshave\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"some restaurant owners\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"80 per cent fewer customers\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"stricter security measures\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Private guide Vadim Sotropa said: \\\"It's important to understand that Parisians' discontent is not directed at the guests or athletes.\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2315, \"end\": 2320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Vadim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.732554421138565e-20, \"text\": \"Vadim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Vadim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Vadim\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians' discontent\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"the guests\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is related to a series of government decisions that failed to balance their ambitious plans with the peaceful lives of the city's residents and country's needs.\\\"\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"government decisions\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"their ambitious plans\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"the peaceful lives\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's residents and country's needs\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, many are leaving the capital during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among them is a designer, who wanted to be identified only as Miranda.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a designer\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"Miranda\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old will be escaping to the south of France for a few days, though she noted that the daily disruptions are minor compared to the plight of certain segments of Paris' population.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999439968335, \"rank\": 2.971633462949277e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2908, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the south\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"the daily disruptions\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2851}, {\"ngram\": \"the plight\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"certain segments\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I feel like these are minor problems as compared to students getting unhoused, homeless people getting shipped off to god knows where and the cops coming to destroy their camping sites, and workers working illegally with no health insurance.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"minor problems\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"homeless people\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"god\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"the cops\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3085}, {\"ngram\": \"their camping sites\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"no health insurance\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am more horrified by the choice of budget that's used for something that's not as important, as compared to using it for something that could help thousands of people.\\\"\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the choice\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"budget\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3341}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A report released in June by the French collective Le Revers de la Medaille (The Other Side of the Medal), which represents 90 non-profit organisations that work with migrants and the homeless, detailed the expulsion of over 12,000 people from Paris since April 2023.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3388, \"end\": 3394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8338435395360055, \"rank\": 0.18708100204884648, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3409, \"end\": 3415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"score\": 0.9999999997830855, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Revers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\"}, {\"begin\": 3599, \"end\": 3604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A report\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3363}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"The Other Side\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3446}, {\"ngram\": \"the Medal\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"90 non-profit organisations\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"migrants\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3530}, {\"ngram\": \"the expulsion\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3571}, {\"ngram\": \"over 12,000 people\", \"from\": 3575, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, there was the controversial decision to spend \\u20ac1.4 billion cleaning the Seine, which will host marathon swimming and the triathlon.\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3702, \"end\": 3707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.394864364328536e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the controversial decision\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon swimming\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3742}, {\"ngram\": \"the triathlon\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Seine will host marathon swimming and the triathlon.\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3767, \"end\": 3772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.394864364328536e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"marathon swimming\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"the triathlon\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: EPA-EFE The installation of an aluminium judging tower for the surfing event in Tahiti also drew ire for its environmental impact - there are concerns about damage to coral reef.\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 4007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3909, \"end\": 3915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999968317752, \"rank\": 3.168096129404832e-09, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3826}, {\"ngram\": \"EPA-EFE The installation\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3852}, {\"ngram\": \"an aluminium judging tower\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3882}, {\"ngram\": \"the surfing event\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3904}, {\"ngram\": \"its environmental impact\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3957}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 3978}, {\"ngram\": \"damage\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 3991}, {\"ngram\": \"coral reef\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not all doom and gloom in Paris, though.\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4041, \"end\": 4046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all doom\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4027}, {\"ngram\": \"gloom\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sotropa and his wife will be attending the opening and closing ceremonies, and will catch events held at iconic venues such as the Eiffel Tower, the Hotel des Invalides, Grand Palais and Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4205, \"end\": 4224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hotel des Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}, {\"begin\": 4243, \"end\": 4263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4822000489619255e-23, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sotropa\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4063}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4076}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening and closing ceremonies\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4152}, {\"ngram\": \"iconic venues\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4174}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 4183, \"to\": 4199}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Palais\", \"from\": 4226, \"to\": 4238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sotropa, 26, admitted that he was not always for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4266, \"to\": 4328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sotropa\", \"from\": 4266, \"to\": 4273}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But now, he said: \\\"I am looking forward to the Olympics because I see it as a unique opportunity to be part of this event.\\\"\", \"from\": 4329, \"to\": 4452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4372, \"to\": 4384}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique opportunity\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4425}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4436}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Describing it as a \\\"once-in-a-lifetime\\\" event, social media content creator Theo Guyon, 23, is happy to soak in the atmosphere, saying: \\\"I am not worried about the crowd, it will just be for a few weeks, and I think the Olympics are worth having for a little less comfort.\\\"\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4530, \"end\": 4534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theseus\", \"score\": 0.9999294321308444, \"rank\": 7.05728492011739e-05, \"text\": \"Theo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theseus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theseus\"}, {\"begin\": 4535, \"end\": 4540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Guyon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0466357066588853e-11, \"text\": \"Guyon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Guyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Guyon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a-lifetime\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4492}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 4566, \"to\": 4580}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4623}, {\"ngram\": \"a few weeks\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4656}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4682}, {\"ngram\": \"a little less comfort\", \"from\": 4704, \"to\": 4725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laurane Vepierre, who usually takes a one-hour commute from the Essonne region to Paris for her job, will be working remotely for most of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4793, \"end\": 4800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essonne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.096268620219718e-29, \"text\": \"Essonne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essonne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essonne\"}, {\"begin\": 4811, \"end\": 4816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Laurane Vepierre\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4745}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-hour commute\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4783}, {\"ngram\": \"her job\", \"from\": 4821, \"to\": 4828}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 4879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she will watch the swimming or athletics events if the opportunity arises.\", \"from\": 4881, \"to\": 4959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the swimming or athletics events\", \"from\": 4900, \"to\": 4932}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 4936, \"to\": 4951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It happens at a different place every four years, so there are benefits for the different places in terms of reputation, image and economy,\\\" said Vepierre.\", \"from\": 4961, \"to\": 5117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different place\", \"from\": 4976, \"to\": 4993}, {\"ngram\": \"benefits\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5033}, {\"ngram\": \"the different places\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5058}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"reputation\", \"from\": 5071, \"to\": 5081}, {\"ngram\": \"image\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5088}, {\"ngram\": \"economy\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5100}, {\"ngram\": \"Vepierre\", \"from\": 5108, \"to\": 5116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it's the Olympics, it's a very cool atmosphere, sport always brings people together.\\\"\", \"from\": 5119, \"to\": 5209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5129, \"to\": 5141}, {\"ngram\": \"a very cool atmosphere\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5170}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5177}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5192, \"to\": 5198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for the legacy of the Paris Games, that remains to be seen, as Sotropa added: \\\"I believe that it will take a long time after the Paris Olympic Games have concluded to objectively assess their benefits or drawbacks, once the excitement has settled and the city has returned to its normal rhythm.\\\"\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5228}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 5232, \"to\": 5247}, {\"ngram\": \"Sotropa\", \"from\": 5277, \"to\": 5284}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5332}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5362}, {\"ngram\": \"their benefits\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5414}, {\"ngram\": \"drawbacks\", \"from\": 5418, \"to\": 5427}, {\"ngram\": \"the excitement\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5448}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 5465, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"its normal rhythm\", \"from\": 5490